进店领豆 = type=cron,cronexp="5 0 * * *",wake-system=1,timeout=3600,script-path=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mudori/Surge/master/Script/jd_scripts/jd_shop.js
京东极速版红包 = type=cron,cronexp="100 0,22 * * *",wake-system=1,timeout=3600,script-path=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mudori/Surge/master/Script/jd_scripts/jd_speed_redpocke.js
